<br>
I think we will get something, but I wouldn't expect it in the next patch, or even the next month of patches necessarily.<br>
<br>
They also mentioned that they might have gone too far in improving DPS on 2-handers and that dual wield may be a little underpowered in comparison, but it didn't sound like they had a plan on that yet either.  They also mentioned that they greatly reduced ripostes by mobs in a recent patch.  I don't know if it was mentioned in any patch messages but I didn't know about it.  Should be helpful to tanks that prefer DW or don't have a good taunting 2-hander.<br>
<br>
I tried to ask them about Furious Bash and whether it was working as intended and whether it affected aggro procs but they never called on me and my arm got tired after a while hehe. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325267">Brutul Vilesilencer</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
